{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/testoptionisolatedirs"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/testOptionIsolateDirs","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"testOptionIsolateDirs"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates a unique temporary directory for each unit test and uses sets"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"XDG directories to point into subdirectories of it for the duration of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the unit test. The directory tree is cleaned up after the test finishes","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"successfully."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that this doesn’t take effect until [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.test_run"},{"text":"] is called,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"so calls to (for example) [func","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.get_home_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] will return the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"system-wide value when made in a test program’s "},{"code":"main()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" function."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following functions will return subdirectories of the temporary directory"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"when this option is used. The specific subdirectory paths in use are not","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"guaranteed to be stable API — always use a getter function to retrieve them.","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.get_home_dir"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_cache_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.get_system_config_dirs"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.get_user_config_dir"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_system_data_dirs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_data_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_state_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_runtime_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The subdirectories may not be created by the test harness; as with normal","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"calls to functions like [func","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_cache_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"], the caller must"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"be prepared to create the directory if it doesn’t exist."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"var","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:4GLib21testOptionIsolateDirsSSvp","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"testOptionIsolateDirs","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"roleHeading":"Global Variable","title":"testOptionIsolateDirs"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A value that can be passed as an option to [func"},{"code":"GLib.test_init","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/testOptionIsolateDirs":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"testOptionIsolateDirs","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/testOptionIsolateDirs","title":"testOptionIsolateDirs","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"A value that can be passed as an option to [func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.test_init"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/testoptionisolatedirs","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib"}}}